1. Core dependencies:


```shellscript
npm install next@latest react@latest react-dom@latest
```

2. Tailwind CSS (for styling):


```shellscript
npm install -D tailwindcss@latest postcss@latest autoprefixer@latest
```

3. shadcn/ui components (which use Radix UI and Tailwind CSS):


```shellscript
npm install @radix-ui/react-avatar @radix-ui/react-slot @radix-ui/react-tabs
npm install class-variance-authority clsx tailwind-merge
```

4. Lucide React (for icons):


```shellscript
npm install lucide-react
```

5. Additional UI components we've used:


```shellscript
npm install @radix-ui/react-progress @radix-ui/react-checkbox
```

6. For form handling (if needed):


```shellscript
npm install react-hook-form
```

7. For animations (if needed):


```shellscript
npm install framer-motion
```

8. For date handling (if needed):


```shellscript
npm install date-fns
``` 
